Directed by Thomas M. Wright

Written by Thomas M. Wright

Star Joel Edgerton(Mark Frame). Sean Harris(Henry Teague). Jada Alberts(Kate Rylett). Cormac Wright(Son). Steve Mouzakis(Paul Emery). Matthew Sunderland(Controller). Fletcher Humphrys(Graham Ikin). Alan Dukes(John). Ewen Leslie(Asst. Commissioner Milliken). Gary Waddell(WA Head). Andreas Sobik(Car Dealer). Checc Musolino(WA Controller). Kym Wheare(Man in the Shadows). Spencer Scholz(Shop Assistant). Sean Daley(WA Head Offsider). James McCluskey-Garcia(Detective A). Athanasios Georgas(Detective B). Thomas Aldahn(Uniformed Officer). Violet Rowe(Mari Patrick). Abel Kollie(Nurse). Heath Palumbo(Surveillance Technician). Brett Archer(Crooked Cop). David Ockenden(Arms Dealer). Rachel Burke(Interviewing Detective). Lori Bell(Former Partner). Lotte St. Clair(Emergency Operator (as Lotte St Clair)). Simon Elrahi(Victorian Lieutenant). Adam Morgan(Large Man). Brendan Cooney(Senior Victorian Detective). Johnny Quaremba(Other Member (as John Quaremba)). Ethan Woollaston(Restaurant Patron). Shedrick K. Yarkpai(Surveillance Operative (as Shedrick Yarkpai)). Martha Lott(RSL Manager). Greg Stone(RSL Announcer). Peter Ferris(Senior WA Cop). Stephen Leeder(Airfield Operative). Kym Hanton(Plain Clothed Officer). Jeff Lang(Milliken Offsider). David Wilson(WA Detective). Paul Harvey(Silent Man). Adam Ovadia(Undercover Housekeeper). Chris Duncan(Hyatt Senior Cop). Isabella Albani(Flight Attendant). Terence Crawford(Deputy Commissioner Sewell). Nick Buckland(Arresting Detective). Brendan Rock(Arresting Officer). Clinton Daniels(Tactical Support). Heidi Jo(Senior Forensic Officer). Jason Moore(Forensic Coordinator). Lawrence Cirocco(Member of Press (uncredited)). Michael Constantinou(James Burke (uncredited)). Sebastian Dickins(Normal Man (uncredited)). Anni Finsterer(Female Uniformed Cop (uncredited)). Mike Foenander(Heavy Man (uncredited)). Patty Glavieux(WA Detective (uncredited)). Vassil Malandris(Detective (uncredited)). Brad McCarthy(SES Worker (uncredited)). Matteo Medos(Detective (uncredited)). Gail Morrison(Old Woman (uncredited)). Melanie Munt(Senior Female Detective (uncredited)). Thibul Nettle(SES worker (uncredited)). Lucinda Nicholas(Flight Attendant (uncredited)). Nathan O’Keefe((uncredited)). Olivia Jane Parker(Nurse (uncredited)). Patrick Prior(QLD Police (uncredited)). Nicole Schoen(QLD Police (uncredited)). Peta Shannon(Detective E (uncredited)). Michael Wollner(Police Officer (uncredited)). Bingchen Ye(QLD Police (uncredited))

Language English

Producers Iain Canning. Joel Edgerton. Morgan Emmery. Rachel Gardner. Simon Gillis. Kim Hodgert. Kerry Kohansky-Roberts. Jean-Charles Levy. Thorsten Schumacher. Libby Sharpe. Emile Sherman. Lars Sylvest. Alexandra Taussig

Production Anonymous Content. Blue-Tongue Films. Rocket Science
